<div class="noinclude"><span class="script">template.XULRefElem()</span></div>
<p>An element that displays an image, much like the HTML <a title="https://developer.mozilla.org/en/HTML/element/img" href="/en/HTML/element/img"><code>img</code></a> element. The <span class="script">template.XULAttr("src")</span> attribute can be used to specify the URL of the image.</p>
<p>More information is available in the <a title="en/XUL_Tutorial/Adding_Labels_and_Images" href="/en/XUL_Tutorial/Adding_Labels_and_Images">XUL tutorial</a>.</p>
<dl> <dt>Attributes</dt> <dd><span class="script">template.PrefAnch("a-", "onerror")</span>, <span class="script">template.PrefAnch("a-", "onload")</span>, <span class="script">template.PrefAnch("a-", "src")</span>, <span class="script">template.PrefAnch("a-", "validate")</span></dd>
</dl>
<dl> <dt>Properties</dt> <dd><span class="script">template.PrefAnch("p-", "accessibleType")</span>, <span class="script">template.PrefAnch("p-", "src")</span></dd>
</dl>
<dl> <dt>Style classes</dt> <dd><span class="script">template.PrefAnch("s-", "alert-icon")</span>, <span class="script">template.PrefAnch("s-", "error-icon")</span>, <span class="script">template.PrefAnch("s-", "message-icon")</span>, <span class="script">template.PrefAnch("s-", "question-icon")</span></dd>
</dl>
